### REST Client examples (VSCode extension: REST Client)

@host = http://localhost:4000
@token = REEMPLAZAR_TOKEN

### Registro
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Perfil
GET {{host}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear canal
POST {{host}}/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "general"
}

### Listar canales
GET {{host}}/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear mensaje (senderId ya no se env√≠a: se obtiene del token)
POST {{host}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hola a todos",
  "channelId": 1
}

### Listar mensajes paginados de un canal
GET {{host}}/messages?channelId=1&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Borrar mensaje
DELETE {{host}}/messages/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Health
GET {{host}}/health
